        "Description": "Arnaldo Giordano is a volunteer with the local Church, having spent almost 2 decades in service to his parish.\r\rSadly, temptation got the better of Arnaldo, who posed as the Priest, taking confession from the unsuspecting patrons, which he later used to blackmail his way into the bed of a powerful locals daughter.\r\rTake him out, 47. If possible...try to find some kind of poetic justice for Mr. Giordano&apos;s penchant for screwing around.",
